high_descs: Move forward, close to the desk in front of you.
Pick up the cell phone from in front of the corner lamp.
Face the opposite direction, then go around the bed to the middle of the side of the bed.
Place the phone on the bed, near the side of the bed closest to you.
Turn left and cross the room to the radiator, then turn right and go close to the desk.
Pick up the cell phone that is between the pencil and the wall.
Carry the cell phone back to the center of the bedside.
Place the phone on the bed next to the other phone, closer to the head of the bed.
anns.task_desc: Relocate two cell phones to a bed.

high_descs: Walk up to the wooden desk in front of you.
Pick up the closest phone off of the desk.
Turn right and walk up to the bed, then turn right and walk across the room, turn left and walk towards the door, stop halfway and turn left to face the bed.
Put the phone on the middle of the bed.
Turn left and walk over to the wall, then turn right and walk up to the wooden desk.
Pick up the phone off of the wooden desk.
Walk back over to the bed.
Put the phone on the bed to the left of the phone that's already there
anns.task_desc: Move two phones to a bed.

high_descs: Walk forward to the table.
Pick up the phone.
Turn around and walk to the other side of the room.  Turn left at the dresser and walk toward the door.   Turn left at the middle of the bed and face the bed.
Put the phone on the bed.
Turn left and walk toward the wall.  Turn right at the wall and walk toward the desk.
Pick up the phone on the desk.
Turn around and walk toward the wall.    Turn left at the wall and walk toward the door.  Turn left at the middle of the bed and face the bed.
Put the phone on the bed to the left of the other phone.
anns.task_desc: Put two phones on the bed.
